original_title: Stevie Wonder - Live at Wembley Stadium - London England 1989
overview: Stevie Wonder's birthday concert, May 14th 1989. Stevie Wonder 's concert special builds up to the highlight of the evening when more than 15 international stars including Tears for Fears, Billy Ocean , Aswad, Cyndi Lauper , Chaka Khan and Junior Giscombe join him on stage to take part in the biggest pop birthday bash this year.
title: Stevie Wonder - Live at Wembley Stadium - London England 1989
